name: FlyingCow
description:
Thank you for your support!

We at REDTRA.GAMES are proud to present our latest game, "Flying Cow," a thrilling twist on the classic Flappy Bird gameplay. In this game, you control a flying farm with a cow as it avoids tornados and storms in the air. With simple controls and challenging gameplay, "Flying Cow" is sure to provide hours of entertainment.

Thank you for visiting REDTRA.GAMES. We hope you enjoy "Flying Cow" and stay tuned for more exciting games from our team!
